%description
Routines to perform estimation and inference under the multivariate
t-distribution. Currently, the following methodologies are implemented:
multivariate mean and covariance estimation, hypothesis testing about the
mean, equicorrelation and homogeneity of variances, the Wilson-Hilferty
transformation, QQ-plots with envelopes and random variate generation.
Some auxiliary functions are also provided.

